OL,3,CMan charged following axe incident and
OL,4,Cfire at petrol station
OL,6,FA man has been arrested and charged
OL,7,Fwith several offences, following a
OL,8,Ffire at a Hampshire petrol station.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,11,FBP garage on Broom Way, Lee-on-the-
OL,12,FSolent, at 11:15am on 4 December 2025,
OL,13,Fafter a man had reportedly been seen
OL,14,Fon the forecourt with an axe.
OL,16,FA fire then broke out at one of the
OL,17,Fpumps, spreading to several vehicles.
OL,19,FHampshire Police, Hampshire & Isle of
OL,20,FWight Fire Service and South Central
OL,21,FAmbulance Service all attended.
