OL,3,CMan charged following axe incident and
OL,4,Cfire at petrol station
OL,6,FA man was located with burn injuries
OL,7,Fand taken to hospital. Police have
OL,8,Fconfirmed that a dog was also found
OL,9,Fdead at the scene.
OL,11,F51-year-old Tyson Charlie Nevin, of
OL,12,FSpicewood in Fareham, was subsequently
OL,13,Farrested in connection with the
OL,14,Fincident.
OL,16,FHe has now been charged with arson
OL,17,Fwith intent to endanger life, arson,
OL,18,Fthreatening a person with a bladed
OL,19,Farticle in a public place, and causing
OL,20,Funnecessary suffering to a protected
OL,21,Fanimal.
